esidents of the United States]]\n[[Category:Second Party System]]\n[[Category:Speakers of the United States House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:Tennessee Democrats]]\n[[Category:Tennessee lawyers]]\n[[Category:Tennessee Jacksonians]]\n[[Category:Candidates in the 1844 United States presidential election]]\n[[Category:1840 United States vice-presidential candidates]]\n[[Category:University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill alumni]]\n", "name_user": "67.187.71.243", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_K._Polk"}
{"title_page": "Damian Schulz", "text_new": "{{short description|Polish volleyball player}}\n{{Infobox volleyball biography\n| name           = Damian Schulz\n| image          = \n| image_size     =\n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Damian Schulz\n| nickname       = ''Bocian''\n| nationality    = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Poland|Polish]]\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|1990|2|26|mf=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[L\u0119bork]], [[Poland]]\n| hometown       = \n| height         = 2.08 m\n| weight         = 95 kg\n| spike          = 355 cm\n| block          = \n| college        = \n| position       = Opposite\n| currentclub    = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]]\n| currentnumber  = 77\n| years          = <br>2011\u20132012<br>2012\u20132013<br>2013\u20132014<br>2014\u20132018<br>2018\u2013\n| teams          = {{flagicon|POL}} SPS L\u0119bork<br> {{flagicon|POL}} Joker Pi\u0142a<br> {{flagicon|POL}} AZS UAM Pozna\u0144<br> {{flagicon|POL}} KPS Siedlce<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]]\n| nationalyears  = 2015\u2013\n| nationalteam   = {{vb|POL}}\n| medaltemplates = \n{{MedalCountry|{{POL}}}}\n{{MedalSport|Men's [[volleyball]]}}\n{{MedalCompetition|[[FIVB Volleyball Men's World Championship|FIVB World Championship]]}}\n{{MedalGold|[[2018 FIVB Volleyball Men's World Championship|2018 Bulgaria/Italy]]|}}\n}}\n\n'''Damian Schulz''' (born 26 February 1990) is a [[Poland|Polish]] [[volleyball player]], a member of [[Poland men's national volleyball team]] and Polish club [[Asseco Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w]], [[2018 FIVB Volleyball Men's World Championship|2018 FIVB World Champion]].\n\n==Career==\n\n===Clubs===\nOn April 19, 2015 [[Lotos Trefl Gda\u0144sk]], including Schulz, achieved [[2014\u201315 Polish Cup of men's volleyball|Polish Cup 2015]].<ref>[http://www.assecoresovia.pl/en/news/art379,polish-cup-for-lotos-trefl-asseco-resovia-in-the-second-place.html#.VVXvK5Mm-9I ''Polish Cup for Lotos Trefl. Asseco Resovia in the second place''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518085144/http://www.assecoresovia.pl/en/news/art379,polish-cup-for-lotos-trefl-asseco-resovia-in-the-second-place.html#.VVXvK5Mm-9I |date=2015-05-18 }} \u2013 assecoresovia.pl \u2013 19-04-2015</ref><ref>[http://www.worldofvolley.com/News/Latest_news/Poland/50923/polish-cup-m-earthquake-at-ergo-arena---lotos-trefl-lifted-trophy-video.html ''POLISH CUP M: Earthquake at Ergo Arena \u2013 Lotos Trefl lifted trophy! (VIDEO)''] \u2013 worldofvolley.com \u2013 19-04-2015</ref> Then he won silver medal of [[2014\u201315 PlusLiga|Polish Championship]].<ref>[http://www.worldofvolley.com/News/Latest_news/Poland/51403/pol-m-madhouse-in-rzeszw--resovia-is-new-polish-champion.html ''POL M: Madhouse in Rzesz\u00f3w \u2013 Resovia is new Polish champion!''] \u2013 worldfovolley.com \u2013 28-04-2015</ref>\n\n===National team===\nHe was appointed to wide squad of [[Poland men's national volleyball team|Polish national team]] in 2015.<ref>[http://www.pzps.pl/Kadra-Narodowa-Siatkarzy-na-2015.html ''Kadra Narodowa Siatkarzy na 2015''] \u2013 pzps.pl \u2013 02-04-2015</ref> \n\nOn September 30, 2018 Poland achieved 3rd title as the [[2018 FIVB Volleyball Men's World Championship|World Champion]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Poland triumph over Brazil to retain World title for years more years |url=http://italy-bulgaria2018.fivb.com/en/news/poland-triumph-over-brazil-to-retain-world?id=79190 |website=FIVB |accessdate=30 September 2018}}</ref>. Poland beat Brazil in the finale 3-0 and defended the title from 2014.\n\n==Sporting achievements==\n* '''National championships'''\n** '''2014/2015''' [[File:Simple gold cup.svg|16px]] [[2014\u201315 Polish Cup of men's volleyball|Polish Cup]], with [[Lotos Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n** '''2014/2015''' [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2014\u201315 PlusLiga|Polish Championship]], with [[Lotos Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n** '''2015/2016''' [[File:Simple gold cup.svg|16px]] Polish SuperCup, with [[Lotos Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n** '''2017/2018''' [[File:Simple gold cup.svg|16px]] [[2017\u201318 Polish Cup of men's volleyball|Polish Cup]], with [[Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n** '''2017/2018''' [[File:Bronze medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2017\u201318 PlusLiga|Polish Championship]], with [[Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n\n* '''National team'''\n** '''2018''' [[File:Gold medal world centered-2.svg|16px]] [[2018 FIVB Volleyball Men's World Championship|FIVB World Championship]]\n\n===Individually===\n* '''2018:''' [[2017\u201318 Polish Cup of men's volleyball|Polish Cup]] \u2013 Most Valuable Player\n\n===State awards===\n* '''2018''' [[File:POL Z\u0142oty Krzy\u017c Zas\u0142ugi BAR.svg|60px|Ribbon]] [[Cross of Merit (Poland)|Gold Cross of Merit]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Odznaczenia dla Mistrz\u00f3w \u015awiata w Pi\u0142ce Siatkowej M\u0119\u017cczyzn 2018 |url=http://www.prezydent.pl/aktualnosci/ordery-i-odznaczenia/art,313,odznaczenia-dla-mistrzow-swiata-w-pilce-siatkowej-mezczyzn-2018.html |website=prezydent.pl |accessdate=2 October 2018 |language=pl |date=2 October 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.plusliga.pl/players/id/704 PlusLiga player profile]\n\n{{commons}}\n{{Poland men volleyball team 2018 FIVB World Championship}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Schulz, Damian}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from L\u0119bork]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Pomeranian Voivodeship]]\n[[Category:Polish men's volleyball players]]\n[[Category:Trefl Gda\u0144sk players]]\n[[Category:Resovia Rzesz\u00f3w players]]\n\n{{Poland-volleyball-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Polish volleyball player}}\n{{Infobox volleyball biography\n| name           = Damian Schulz\n| image          = \n| image_size     =\n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Damian Schulz\n| nickname       = ''Bocian''\n| nationality    = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Poland|Polish]]\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|